snippet.title: Luigi's Quest - Trailer
snippet.description:
Luigi's Quest is a mini mod of New Super Mario Bros. Wii based on the mod Super Luigi Land Wii.

Thanks to Rimea for showcasing the trailer of my mod in the New Super Mario Bros. Franchise Modding Direct!
Thanks to my friends for the help!
Thanks to the New Luigi Team for the original Super Luigi Land Wii mod.
Thanks to the Evolution Discord server for the help!
Logo by Rimea.
